TITLE: Updating a Shipment with Python
DESCRIPTION: Updates a shipment's properties using the Karrio API with Python. This example shows how to modify a shipment's label type, reference, payment details, options, and add metadata.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/reference/api/update-shipment.api.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
import karrio

client = karrio.Karrio(
    api_key="API_KEY",
    host="https://api.karrio.io",
)

request = {
    "shipment_identifier": "shp_c0a5c06c6c55458997b67dd7ad56e740",
    "shipment": {
        "label_type": "PDF",
        "reference": "my-reference",
        "payment": {
            "paid_by": "sender",
            "currency": "CAD",
            "account_number": "2343253"  
        },
        "options": {
            "shipment_date": "2022-09-12"
        },
        "metadata": {
            "source": "web"
        }
    }
}

response = client.shipments.update(request)

print(response)
```

