TITLE: Complete Example of Fetching Tracking Details with Karrio API in Python
DESCRIPTION: This code sample provides a complete example of how to use the Karrio API to fetch tracking details for a specific package. It initializes a TrackingRequest with a tracking number, sends the request, and parses the response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/carriers/sdk/tracking.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
import karrio
from karrio.core.models import TrackingRequest

request = karrio.Tracking.fetch(
    TrackingRequest(tracking_numbers=["1Z12345E6205277936"])
)

tracking_details_list, messages = request.from_(carrier_gateway).parse()
```

