TITLE: Creating Carrier Connection using GraphQL
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a GraphQL mutation for creating a carrier connection with the specified input data. It requires a `CreateCarrierConnectionMutationInput` object containing carrier-specific details like `carrier_id`, `sendle_id`, `api_key`, and more. The mutation handles errors by returning a list of fields and messages, if any. The expected output includes potential error messages related to the creation process.
