TITLE: Sending GraphQL Requests with JavaScript Fetch
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet demonstrates how to send a GraphQL request to the Karrio Management API using the Fetch API. It sets the 'Authorization' and 'Content-Type' headers and passes the GraphQL query and variables in the request body as a JSON string.  The 'mode' and 'credentials' options are also specified.
