DESCRIPTION: Details a schema item for the first line of an address, combining street number and name, defined as a nullable string capped at 50 characters. This entry is vital for shipment purchase operations as it serves as a mandatory address specification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/reference/api/purchase.api.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{"type":"string","nullable":true,"description":"The address line with street number <br>\n        **(required for shipment purchase)**\n        ","maxLength":50}
```

