TITLE: Querying System Connections with GraphQL
DESCRIPTION: This GraphQL query retrieves details of system connections, including their ID, carrier information, capabilities, and configuration status. It returns an array of connection objects with various properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/reference/management/connections.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
query getSystemConnections {
  system_connections {
    id
    carrier_id
    test_mode
    active
    capabilities
    carrier_name
    display_name
    enabled
    config
  }
}
```

