TITLE: Displaying Documentation Card List with Docusaurus
DESCRIPTION: This snippet imports and uses Docusaurus components to dynamically generate a list of documentation cards based on the current sidebar category.  It relies on `@theme/DocCardList` and `@docusaurus/theme-common` for rendering the card list and accessing the current sidebar category, respectively. The `<DocCardList>` component takes an `items` prop, which is populated with the items from the current sidebar category obtained via `useCurrentSidebarCategory().items`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/reference/api/shipments.tag.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: mdx
CODE:
```
import DocCardList from '@theme/DocCardList';
import {useCurrentSidebarCategory} from '@docusaurus/theme-common';

<DocCardList items={useCurrentSidebarCategory().items}/>
```

