CODE:
```
import attr
import jstruct
import typing

@attr.s(auto_attribs=True)
class PersonType:
    first_name: typing.Optional[str] = None
    last_name: typing.Optional[str] = None

@attr.s(auto_attribs=True)
class RoleModelsType:
    scientists: typing.Optional[typing.List[PersonType]] = jstruct.JList[PersonType]
```

