LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
                            <SchemaItem
                              collapsible={false}
                              name={"content"}
                              required={false}
                              schemaName={"string"}
                              qualifierMessage={"**Possible values:** `<= 100 characters`"}
                              schema={{"type":"string","nullable":true,"description":"The parcel's content description","maxLength":100}}
                            >
```

