DESCRIPTION: This code snippet imports integration data from a JSON file and a custom React component. It then renders the CarrierIntegrationDetails component with Purolator-specific information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/carriers/integrations/purolator.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_0

