TITLE: Defining Optional Reference Number Schema in React JSX
DESCRIPTION: Specifies a schema item for a parcel reference number which can be used for tracking and is limited to 100 characters. The field is nullable with a description of its utility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/karrioapi/karrio/blob/main/apps/www/docs/reference/api/list-parcels.api.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: React JSX
CODE:
```
schema={{"type":"string","nullable":true,"description":"The parcel reference number.<br/>\n        (can be used as tracking number for custom carriers)\n        ","maxLength":100}}
```

